{"tid":82792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"司機疑不適暈倒 巴士直撞吊臂6人傷","createTime":"2017-01-16T08:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T08:36:10.000Z","uid":35107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8719e29fac1b7006ed03d4d9c29b26f73ef2c35","tid":82792,"uid":35107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170116/56180468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170116%2F56180468&d=GUD5MvgjgrmcxETNPgbuAXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b1c65fde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170116%2F56180468&h=ad84325f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170116/56180468</a><br />\n藍田鯉魚門道1死18傷車禍發生才兩天，再有巴士司機懷疑身體不適撞車。下午2時55分，一輛九巴沿荃灣路出九龍，至晉昇工業中心附近，巴士司機突然不適暈倒，巴士直撞前面一輛由貨櫃拖架載運的吊臂車伸出的吊臂。巴士整塊擋風玻璃碎裂，車上5、6名乘客受傷。"}]}